  "question": "<span class=\"TextRun SCXW112065298 BCX8\" lang=\"EN-GB\" xml:lang=\"EN-GB\" data-contrast=\"auto\"><span class=\"NormalTextRun SCXW112065298 BCX8\"> Which among the following are the types of Justice identified by Aristotle?</span></span><span class=\"EOP SCXW112065298 BCX8\" data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335559685&quot;:360,&quot;335559739&quot;:160,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}\"> </span>",
  "option1": "Distributive Justice",
  "option2": "Retributive Justice",
  "option3": "Commutative justice",
  "option4": "All of the above",
  "option5": "",
  "answer": "All of the above",
  "explanation": "<p><span data-contrast=\"auto\">Aristotle has identified three </span><span data-contrast=\"auto\">distinct</span><span data-contrast=\"auto\"> types of </span><span data-contrast=\"auto\">justice</span><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335559685&quot;:360,&quot;335559739&quot;:160,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}\"> </span></p>\r\n<span data-contrast=\"auto\">1. Distributive justice which is the concern of a legislator and deals with allocation of honours and wealth</span><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;134233279&quot;:true,&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335559739&quot;:160,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}\"> </span><br /><span data-contrast=\"auto\">2. Retributive justice is concerned of judiciary and deals with imposition of punishment and payment of damages</span><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;134233279&quot;:true,&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335559739&quot;:160,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}\"> 3.</span><br /><span data-contrast=\"auto\">3. Commutative justice is also the concern of a judge and deals with </span><span data-contrast=\"auto\">regulation</span><span data-contrast=\"auto\"> of </span><span data-contrast=\"auto\">voluntary</span><span data-contrast=\"auto\"> transaction.</span><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;134233279&quot;:true,&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335559739&quot;:160,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}\"> </span>"
}